Aquarium plants are more than mere adornments; they are the natural counterpart to fishes in a truly balanced system. Which plants should you choose? How can you grow them successfully?. This colorful guide provides a wealth of practical advice plus a detailed survey of more than 60 freshwater aquarium plants
